{{main|飓风鲍勃}}
飓风鲍勃源自一股正在衰减的[[冷锋|冷锋]]，于8月16日清晨在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]附近发展成热带低气压<ref name="TCR1">{{cite web |author=Max Mayfield |publisher=National Hurricane Center |date=1992-08-10 |accessdate=2014-02-21 |title=Hurricane Bob Preliminary Report (Page One) |archivedate=2012-10-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023133230/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim01.gif |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim01.gif |format=GIF }}</ref>。低气压产生了一片有组织的对流区，于形成约18小时后增强为热带风暴，美国国家飓风中心因此将其命名为鲍勃（{{lang|en|Bob}}）<ref name="TCR1" />。风暴在[[墨西哥湾暖流|墨西哥湾暖流]]的利好条件下逐渐组织起来<ref>{{cite web |author=Lixion A. Avila |publisher=National Hurricane Center |date=1991-08-17 |accessdate=2014-02-21 |title=Tropical Storm Bob Discussion Five |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/tropdisc/nal0391.005 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023133443/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/tropdisc/nal0391.005 |archivedate=2012-10-23 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，根据[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]][[侦察机|侦察机]]的报告{{#tag:ref|从[[1944年大西洋飓风季|1944年大西洋飓风季]]开始，[[美国空军预备役司令部|美国空军预备役司令部]]就会派出侦察机飞入热带风暴和飓风进行观察并提交报告，飓风猎人就是这些侦察机中的一部分。<ref>{{cite web |publisher=National Hurricane Center |date=2011-08-11 |title=NHC Aircraft Reconnaissance |accessdate=2014-02-21 |archivedate=2013-12-16 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216231935/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/recon.php |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/recon.php }}</ref>|group="注"}}，鲍勃于8月17日达到飓风强度<ref name="TCR1" />。此后不久，飓风由于受到大西洋上空一片副热带高压脊和美国东南部上空[[低压槽|低压槽]]的影响开始转向东北偏北<ref name="TCR2">{{cite web |author=Max Mayfield |publisher=National Hurricane Center |date=1992-08-10 |accessdate=2014-02-21 |title=Hurricane Bob Preliminary Report (Page Two) |archivedate=2012-10-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023133450/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim02.gif |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim02.gif |format=GIF }}</ref>。之后在[[南卡罗莱纳州|南]]、[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]近海继续增强，于8月19日在弗吉尼亚州以东洋面达到每小时185公里的最高风速，这已经到达了大型飓风的标准。接下来由于进入了一片[[海面温度|海面温度]]大幅降低的海域，飓风开始减弱。掠过纽约州长岛后，鲍勃的中心移动到了罗德岛州布洛克岛上空，并在40分钟后以风速每小时155公里的二级飓风强度袭击了该州的纽波特。系统在继续穿越新英格兰其他地区的过程中快速减弱，于8月20日清晨吹袭了[[诺克斯县_(缅因州)|诺克斯县]]小镇罗克波特（{{lang|en|Rockport}}）。穿过[[新不伦瑞克|新不伦瑞克]]后，鲍勃在[[圣罗伦斯湾|圣罗伦斯湾]]转变成温带气旋并持续了九天，最终在[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]以西海域消散。<ref name="TCR2" />

这场飓风起初对南、北卡罗莱纳州产生了影响，在北卡罗莱纳州催生了多个[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，其中得到确认的就有4个，另外还有9个未经确认<ref name="TCR3">{{cite web |author=Max Mayfield |publisher=National Hurricane Center |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025172307/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim03.gif |date=1992-08-10 |accessdate=2011-07-12 |title=Hurricane Bob Preliminary Report (Page Three) |archivedate=2012-10-25 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim03.gif |format=GIF |deadurl=no }}</ref>。两州各有一人死亡<ref name="TCR4_04">{{cite web |author=Max Mayfield |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029203914/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim04.gif |publisher=National Hurricane Center |date=1992-08-10 |accessdate=2011-07-12 |title=Hurricane Bob Preliminary Report (Page Four) |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/bob/prelim04.gif |format=GIF |archivedate=2013-10-29 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，[[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]]约10%的房屋受到了轻度损伤<ref>{{cite web |author=Wallace Demaurice |publisher=Cape Hatteras NC National Weather Service |date=1991-08-20 |title=Preliminary Report Hurricane Bob |accessdate=2014-02-21 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/hat.gif |format=GIF |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025172316/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/hat.gif |archivedate=2012-10-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。沿海岸行进时，风暴中心的西面产生了暴雨<ref name="brain">{{cite web |author=David Roth |date=2007-04-30 |title=Hurricane Bob — August 18–21, 1991 |publisher=Hydrometeorological Prediction Center |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130922024202/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/bob1991.html |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-09-22 |accessdate=2014-02-21 |url=http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/bob1991.html }}</ref>。狂风导致纽约州长岛有30万人失去电力供应<ref>{{cite web |author=FEMA Headquarters |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |title=Situation Report — Hurricane Bob |year=1991 |accessdate=2014-02-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029190408/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/fema01.gif |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/fema01.gif |format=GIF |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-10-29 }}</ref>。附近的[[康涅狄格州|康涅狄格州]]有许多树木被风刮倒，其中东南部沿岸地区受损最为严重<ref>{{cite web |author=Hartford, CT National Weather Service |date=1991-08-23 |title=Preliminary Survey Hurricane Bob... Final Issue |accessdate=2014-02-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025172352/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshbdl1.gif |deadurl=no |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshbdl1.gif |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |format=GIF |archivedate=2012-10-25 }}</ref>。鲍勃最后一次登陆时造成了最为沉重的打击<ref name="tcr3" />，罗德岛州布洛克岛报告了时速168公里的阵风<ref name="tcr3" />。飓风导致了大面积[[海岸侵蚀|海滩侵蚀]]，罗德岛州的沉海公路也遭摧毁<ref>{{cite web |author=David R. Vallee and Paul Sisson |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshpvd06.gif |format=GIF |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025172412/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/bob/preloc/pshpvd06.gif |archivedate=2012-10-25 |accessdate=2014-02-21 |date=1991-08-23 |title=Preliminary Survey on Hurricane Bob |publisher=Providence RI National Weather Service }}</ref>。[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]受到的经济损失最为严重<ref name="TCR4_04"/>，鲍勃途经的新英格兰东南部地区有超过60%的人失去电力供应。大浪和强风毁坏了马萨诸塞州沿海的船只和房屋<ref>{{cite web |author=David R. Vallee and Michael R. Dion |publisher=Boston, MA National Weather Service |url=http://www.erh.noaa.gov/box/hurricane/hurricaneBob.shtml |accessdate=2011-07-12 |title=Hurricane Bob |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130615032341/http://www.erh.noaa.gov/box/hurricane/hurricaneBob.shtml |archivedate=2013-06-15 }}</ref>。缅因州的[[波特兰国际喷射机机场|波特兰国际喷射机机场]]在飓风经过期间降雨量达209毫米，比其他任何地区都要高<ref name="brain" />。整个美国因这场飓风遭受了15亿美元（1991年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|1500000000|1991}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）的损失<ref name="TCR4_04"/>，其中单马萨诸塞州就超过10亿美元（1991年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|1000000000|1991}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）<ref name="end" />，成为当时美国历史上造成损失最惨重的十场飓风之一。此外，全美还有15人丧生<ref name="TCR4_04"/>。加拿大有两人因风暴产生的大浪遇难<ref name="TS2">{{cite news |author=Associated Press |work=Toronto Star |date=1991-08-20 |accessdate=2014-02-21 |title=Storm sweeps 2 teens to sea 'The wave just sucked them away . . . The ocean was wild' |page=A3 |url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/thestar/doc/436456160.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Aug%2020,%201991&author=Staff-CP-AP&pub=Toronto%20Star&edition=&startpage=&desc=Storm%20sweeps%202%20teens%20to%20sea%20'The%20wave%20just%20sucked%20them%20away%20.%20.%20.%20The%20ocean%20was%20wild' |archive-date=2017-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171025155252/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/thestar/doc/436456160.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Aug%2020,%201991&author=Staff-CP-AP&pub=Toronto%20Star&edition=&startpage=&desc=Storm%20sweeps%202%20teens%20to%20sea%20%27The%20wave%20just%20sucked%20them%20away%20.%20.%20.%20The%20ocean%20was%20wild%27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。热带风暴强度的大风刮倒了新不伦瑞克[[弗雷德里克顿|弗雷德里克顿]]的许多树木，导致多条供电线路中断<ref name="TS1">{{cite news |author=Associated Press |work=Toronto Star |date=1991-08-20 |accessdate=2014-02-21 |title=Hurricane Bob lashes coast 2 swept out to sea as storm hits Nova Scotia |page=A3 |url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/thestar/doc/436457999.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Aug%2020,%201991&author=CP-AP&pub=Toronto%20Star&edition=&startpage=&desc=Hurrican%20Bob%20lashes%20coast%202%20swept%20out%20to%20sea%20as%20storm%20hits%20Nova%20Scotia |archive-date=2016-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827192400/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/thestar/doc/436457999.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&type=current&date=Aug%2020,%201991&author=CP-AP&pub=Toronto%20Star&edition=&startpage=&desc=Hurrican%20Bob%20lashes%20coast%202%20swept%20out%20to%20sea%20as%20storm%20hits%20Nova%20Scotia |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

