克劳德特源自于9月4日百慕大东南方向约1000公里海域的一片上层扰动<ref name="Prem1">{{cite web |author=Richard Pasch |year=1991 |title=Hurricane Claudette Preliminary Report |archivedate=2012-10-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025084944/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/claudett/prenhc/prelim01.gif |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/claudett/prenhc/prelim01.gif |deadurl=no |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2014-02-21 }}</ref>。系统缓慢向东南方向移动并逐渐发展<ref name="Prem1" />，于9月5日达到热带风暴强度并由美国国家飓风中心命名为克劳德特（{{lang|en|Claudette}}）<ref>{{cite web |author=Miles Lawrence |date=1991-09-05 |title=Tropical Storm Claudette Public Advisory Four |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025084951/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/claudett/public/pal0691.004 |archivedate=2012-10-25 |deadurl=no |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2014-02-21 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/claudett/public/pal0691.004 }}</ref>。外界环境有利于系统发展，风切变较弱，而且还有一个大规模的反气旋提供[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]，即风暴向外流动的风<ref name="Prem1" />。到了{{lang|en|UTC}}9月6日早上6点，风暴达到飓风强度<ref>{{cite web |author=Miles Lawrence |date=1991-09-06 |title=Hurricane Claudette Public Advisory Eight |publisher=National Hurricane Center |archivedate=2012-10-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025085011/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/claudett/public/pal0691.008 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/claudett/public/pal0691.008 |accessdate=2010-01-04 }}</ref>，然后开始进入急速增强阶段，到了9月7日清晨，一架侦察机报告克劳德特已经达到大型飓风强度，风力时速有185公里<ref name="Prem1" /><ref>{{cite web |author=Miles Lawrence |date=1991-09-06 |title=Hurricane Claudette Public Advisory Nine |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/claudett/public/pal0691.009 |accessdate=2010-01-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025085016/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/claudett/public/pal0691.009 |archivedate=2012-10-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。根据卫星数据估算，飓风克劳德特达到的最高强度为风速每小时215公里，最低气压946毫巴（百帕，27.9英寸汞柱）<ref name="Prem2">{{cite web |author=Richard Pasch |year=1991 |title=Hurricane Claudette Preliminary Report (Page 2) |archivedate=2012-10-25 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025085021/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/claudett/prenhc/prelim02.gif |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/claudett/prenhc/prelim02.gif |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2014-02-21 }}</ref>。

达到最高强度后，克劳德特开始稳步减弱<ref name="Prem5"/>，当时百慕大已经收到了[[热带气旋警告|飓风观察预警]]，并在之后升级为飓风警告<ref name="Prem3">{{cite web |author=Richard Pasch |year=1991 |title=Hurricane Claudette Preliminary Report (Page 3) |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2014-02-21 |archivedate=2012-10-25 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025085036/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/claudett/prenhc/prelim03.gif |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/claudett/prenhc/prelim03.gif }}</ref>。飓风转向西北，于9月8日以一级飓风强度在百慕大以东约219公里海域经过<ref>{{cite web |author=Miles Lawrence |date=1991-09-09 |title=Hurricane Claudette Public Advisory Nineteen |publisher=National Hurricane Center |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025085031/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/claudett/public/pal0691.019 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/claudett/public/pal0691.019 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2012-10-25 |accessdate=2014-02-21 }}</ref>。该岛上的最大持续风速为每小时37公里，阵风时速达到51公里，海浪有2.43米高<ref name="Prem3" />。9月10日，克劳德特减弱到热带风暴强度并加速向东移动，次日就进一步减弱为热带低气压，又一天后，系统在亚速尔群岛东南方向转变成温带气旋，并持续了两天后在亚速尔群岛上空消散<ref name="Prem2"/>。
