热带风暴法比安是由10月15日[[加勒比|加勒比]]以西一股冷锋和一股东风波之间的相互作用发展而成。起初系统杂乱无章<ref name="ftcr">{{cite web |author=Lixion Avila |year=1991 |title=Tropical Storm Fabian Preliminary Report (Page One) |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018182803/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/fabian/prenhc/prelim01.gif |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/fabian/prenhc/prelim01.gif |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2014-02-21 |format=GIF |archivedate=2012-10-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，其最强风力主要位于中心以东<ref name="disc2">{{cite web |author=Ed Rappaport |date=1991-10-15 |title=Tropical Storm Fabian Discussion Two |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2014-02-21 |archivedate=2012-10-25 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025164330/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/fabian/tropdisc/nal0991.002 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/fabian/tropdisc/nal0991.002 }}</ref>。一个向东移动的上层槽令系统向东北方向移动，还产生了不利于系统发展的风切变<ref name="disc1">{{cite web |author=Ed Rappaport |date=1991-10-15 |title=Tropical Storm Fabian Discussion One |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2011-07-07 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/fabian/tropdisc/nal0991.001 |archivedate=2012-10-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018182821/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/fabian/tropdisc/nal0991.001 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。法比安达到每小时75公里的最大风速后穿过[[青年岛|青年岛]]，然后继续穿越古巴西部<ref name="ftcr" />，给当地带去了暴雨，其中一个地点在六小时中的降雨量就达到130毫米<ref name="ftcr2">{{cite web |author=Lixion Avila |year=1991 |title=Tropical Storm Fabian Preliminary Report (Page Two) |publisher=National Hurricane Center |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/fabian/prenhc/prelim02.gif |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018182946/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/fabian/prenhc/prelim02.gif |archivedate=2012-10-18 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2011-07-07 |format=GIF }}</ref>。10月16日早上，法比安在经过[[佛罗里达海峡|佛罗里达海峡]]时其中心已经难以定位<ref name="disc3">{{cite web |author=Miles Lawrence |date=1991-10-16 |title=Tropical Storm Fabian Discussion Three |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2014-02-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018182829/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/fabian/tropdisc/nal0991.003 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/fabian/tropdisc/nal0991.003 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2012-10-18 }}</ref>。最终风暴在佛罗里达州东南近海掠过<ref name="ftcr" />，有两个州立[[公园|公园]]为此关闭，[[佛罗里达礁岛群|佛罗里达礁岛群]]中部的海螺礁岛（{{lang|en|Conch Key}}）出现了106毫米降雨<ref>{{cite web |author=David Roth |date=2007-06-11 |title=Tropical Storm Fabian — October 13–16, 1991 |publisher=Hydrometeorological Prediction Center |accessdate=2014-02-21 |url=http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/fabian1991.html |archivedate=2013-09-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130922080311/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/fabian1991.html |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="Key West report">{{cite web |author=Dennis Henize (Key West Weather Forecast Office) |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |title=Post-Storm Report — Preliminary Storm Summary: Tropical Storm Fabian |date=1991-10-17 |accessdate=2014-02-21 |archivedate=2012-10-18 |format=GIF |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018182956/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/fabian/preloc/psheyw.gif |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/fabian/preloc/psheyw.gif }}</ref>。风暴产生的影响很小，[[基韦斯特_(佛罗里达州)|基韦斯特]]的阵风时速为52公里<ref name="Key West report" />。法比安之后朝[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]进发，并在与一个接近的锋相互作用后转变成温带气旋<ref name="ftcr" />。
