{{Main|飓风格雷斯}}
10月23日，百慕大以南海域形成了一片中层低气压，两天后成为表面低气压，并在10月26日发展成[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]。系统中心上空起初缺乏深层对流，但在之后由于雷暴活动有所增强，美国国家飓风中心于10月27日将其重新归类为热带风暴格雷斯。当时风暴总体向西北方向前进<ref name="GTCR1">{{cite web |author=Edward Rappaport |title=Hurricane Grace Preliminary Report (Page One) |date=1991-11-13 |publisher=National Hurricane Center |deadurl=no |accessdate=2009-09-13 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/grace/prelim01.gif |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928024551/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/grace/prelim01.gif |archivedate=2013-09-28 }}</ref>。格雷斯继续加强和组织，美国国家飓风中心根据飓风猎人侦察机的报告于10月28日清晨将风暴升级为飓风<ref name="GTCR2">{{cite web |author=Edward Rappaport |title=Hurricane Grace Preliminary Report (Page Two) |date=1991-11-13 |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2014-02-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928024721/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/grace/prelim02.gif |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/grace/prelim02.gif |archivedate=2013-09-28 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。之后不久，由于[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]近海有有一个温带气旋快速增强，飓风大幅向东转向<ref name="history">{{cite news |author=Chris Cappella |title=1991's 'perfect storm' a hybrid hurricane |date=2005-05-17 |agency=USA Today |accessdate=2014-02-21 |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/wdisguis.htm |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022182602/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/wdisguis.htm |deadurl=no |archivedate=2012-10-22 }}</ref>，虽然对流层仍然薄弱，但格雷斯的中心已经发展出[[风眼|风眼]]<ref>{{cite web |author=Richard Pasch |title=Hurricane Grace Discussion Five |date=1991-10-28 |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2014-02-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928024716/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/grace/tropdisc/nal1191.005 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991/grace/tropdisc/nal1191.005 |archivedate=2013-09-28 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

飓风向东加速移动，于10月29日达到风速每小时155公里的最高强度。由于移动速度快，系统的风场变得不对称，风暴中心在百慕大以南约80公里洋面经过，没有对该岛产生严重影响<ref name="GTCR2" />。10月29日，格雷斯被一股迅速靠近的冷锋吸收<ref name="GTCR3">{{cite web |author=Edward Rappaport |title=Hurricane Grace Preliminary Report (Page Three) |date=1991-11-13 |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2014-02-21 |archivedate=2014-01-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193505/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/grace/prelim03.gif |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/grace/prelim03.gif |deadurl=no }}</ref>，该温带气旋获得了来自格雷斯的湿气，并最终发展成[[1991年完美风暴|完美风暴]]<ref name="history" /><ref name="history2">{{cite web |author=National Climatic Data Center |title=The Perfect Storm |date=2008-08-20 |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-02-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131106033734/http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/satellite/satelliteseye/cyclones/pfctstorm91/pfctstorm.html |url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/satellite/satelliteseye/cyclones/pfctstorm91/pfctstorm.html |archivedate=2013-11-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。飓风格雷斯处于热带气旋期间给整个百慕大带去了狂风<ref>{{cite news |author=Staff Writer |title=Bermuda Braces for Brush with Hurricane Grace |date=1991-10-29 |newspaper=St. Paul Pioneer Press |accessdate=2014-02-21 |url=http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=PD&s_site=twincities&p_multi=SP&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB5DB42D312BD55&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM |archive-date=2011-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110609121856/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=PD&s_site=twincities&p_multi=SP&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB5DB42D312BD55&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但没有出现遭受损失的报告。飓风产生的大浪影响了[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]<ref name="GTCR3" />，导致了轻度海滩侵蚀<ref>{{cite news |author=Staff Writer |title=Hurricane Grace Kicks up Waves, Avoids N.C. Coast |date=1991-10-29 |newspaper=Morning Star |accessdate=2014-02-21 |url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=RNIVAAAAIBAJ&sjid=khQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6366,5152585&dq=hurricane+grace+swells+flood |archive-date=2022-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220424030920/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=RNIVAAAAIBAJ&sjid=khQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6366%2C5152585&dq=hurricane+grace+swells+flood }}</ref>。
