{{Main|1991年完美风暴}}
完美风暴源于10月28日在[[加拿大大西洋省份|加拿大大西洋省份]]近海发展出来的一片低气压区。这时有一个强烈的[[高气压|高气压]]从墨西哥湾东北方向沿[[阿巴拉契亚山脉|阿巴拉契亚山脉]]一直延伸到[[格陵兰|格陵兰]]，高压脊迫使温带低气压朝东南方向行进，之后又转向朝西并达到最高强度。风暴以巨浪和沿海洪灾对美国东岸造成了强烈的冲击，然后转向西北并逐渐减弱<ref name="history2" />。进入水温较高的海域后，系统转变成[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]，然后又变成热带风暴<ref name="8 TCR">{{cite web |author=Richard Pasch |title=Unnamed Hurricane Preliminary Report (Page 1) |date= |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2014-02-21 |archivedate=2012-10-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023203807/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/unnamed/prelim01.gif |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1991-prelim/unnamed/prelim01.gif }}</ref>。风暴在中大西洋各州近海行进了一个环形路径后转向朝东北方向前进，到11月1日已演变成一个完整的飓风，最高风速每小时120公里<ref name="history4">{{cite web |author=National Climatic Data Center |title=Unnamed Hurricane |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-01-20 |archivedate=2013-12-07 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207192407/http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/satellite/satelliteseye/hurricanes/unnamed91/unnamed91.html |url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/satellite/satelliteseye/hurricanes/unnamed91/unnamed91.html }}</ref>。之后该热带系统减弱为热带风暴，并在袭击[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]后消散<ref name="history4" /><ref name="Canada">{{cite web |author=Canadian Hurricane Centre |date=2010-09-14 |title=1991-Unnamed "Perfect Storm" |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005234342/http://www.ec.gc.ca/hurricane/default.asp?lang=En&n=B87EB885-1 |accessdate=2014-01-20 |url=http://www.ec.gc.ca/Hurricane/default.asp?lang=En&n=B87EB885-1 |publisher=Environment Canada |archivedate=2013-10-05 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

这场风暴造成的经济损失总计超过2.08亿美元（1991年美元，相当于{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|208000000|1991}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）<ref name="ncdc">{{cite web |last=McCown |first=Sam |work=National Climatic Data Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |date=2008-08-20 |title="Perfect Storm" Damage Summary |accessdate=2011-06-20 |archivedate=2013-10-22 |url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/satellite/satelliteseye/cyclones/pfctstorm91/pfctstdam.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022095540/http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/satellite/satelliteseye/cyclones/pfctstorm91/pfctstdam.html |deadurl=no }}</ref>，还导致13人丧生<ref name="Canada" /><ref name="erh" />。大部分灾难损失是在风暴还是温带系统时发生的，高达10米的海浪袭击了从加拿大到佛罗里达州以及更东南部的[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]海岸线。[[马萨诸塞州|马萨诸塞州]]受到的打击最为沉重，超过100户民宅被摧毁或严重受损<ref name="ncdc" />。其北面的[[缅因州|缅因州]]也有超过100户家庭受到影响<ref name="maine">{{cite news |first=William C. |last=Hidlay |date=1991-11-01 |title=Maine hit hard by storm |agency=Associated Press |newspaper=Bangor Daily News |accessdate=2014-01-20 |url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=DqhJAAAAIBAJ&sjid=KQ4NAAAAIBAJ&pg=3345,8099&dq=storm+new+england&hl=en |archive-date=2021-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109131111/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=DqhJAAAAIBAJ&sjid=KQ4NAAAAIBAJ&pg=3345%2C8099&dq=storm+new+england&hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>，包括当时[[美国总统|美国总统]][[乔治·赫伯特·沃克·布什|乔治·赫伯特·沃克·布什]]的度假屋<ref name="history2" />。超过38000人家中停电<ref name="ct">{{cite news |author=Staff writer |agency=Associated Press |newspaper=Record-Journal |date=1991-10-31 |title=Wind and water take toll along Connecticut Shore |accessdate=2014-01-20 |url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ihxIAAAAIBAJ&sjid=rgANAAAAIBAJ&pg=1620,180883&dq=storm+new+england&hl=en |archive-date=2021-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108170324/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ihxIAAAAIBAJ&sjid=rgANAAAAIBAJ&pg=1620,180883&dq=storm+new+england&hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>，沿海巨浪导致道路和建筑物被淹<ref name="erh" />。[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]部分地区受到的损失比两个月前的[[飓风鲍勃|飓风鲍勃]]还要严重<ref name="maine" />。不过除了多条河流出现潮汐洪水外，风暴的影响主要集中在沿海地区<ref name="ncdc" />。新斯科舍近海的一个浮标报告了高达30.7米的狂浪，创下该省海域的新纪录<ref name="Canada" />，该海域有一艘名为“安德烈·盖尔号”的渔船及其六名船员在风暴中葬身大海，这一事件写入了畅销书《完美风暴》，之后又改编成[[美国大片|好莱坞]]同名[[大片|大片]]<ref name="history2" /><ref>{{cite news |first=Paula |last=Park |newspaper=Sarasota Herald-Tribune |date=1991-11-11 |title=Search Ended for Lost Fishermen |accessdate=2014-01-20 |url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=y64cAAAAIBAJ&sjid=3HsEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6811,330103&dq=andrea+gail&hl=en |archive-date=2021-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108170410/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=y64cAAAAIBAJ&sjid=3HsEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6811,330103&dq=andrea+gail&hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。纽约[[长岛_(纽约)|长岛]]近海有一架空中国民警卫队[[直升机|直升机]]因油料耗尽而坠毁，不过机上五人中有四人生还，另外一人遇难<ref name="ct" /><ref>{{cite web |first=William H. |last=Thiesen |date=2010-11-04 |title=History – CGC Tamaroa and "The Perfect Storm" |publisher=Coastguard Compass |accessdate=2011-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2011-01-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110116071513/http://coastguard.dodlive.mil/index.php/2010/11/history-cgc-tamaroa-and-%E2%80%9Cthe-perfect-storm%E2%80%9D/ |url=http://coastguard.dodlive.mil/2010/11/history-cgc-tamaroa-and-%E2%80%9Cthe-perfect-storm%E2%80%9D/ }}</ref><ref name="pp">{{cite news |author=Staff writer |agency=Associated Press |newspaper=The Pittsburgh Press |date=1991-10-31 |title=East battered by storm born off Canada; 4 lost |accessdate=2014-01-20 |url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Md8cAAAAIBAJ&sjid=GGQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6189,8218796&dq=storm+new+england&hl=en |archive-date=2021-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108170338/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Md8cAAAAIBAJ&sjid=GGQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6189,8218796&dq=storm+new+england&hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[史泰登岛|史泰登岛]]海域有两人因船只沉没而遇难。罗德岛州和[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]各有一人因被大浪卷走而丧生，还有一人被狂风吹落桥下而死亡<ref name="ncdc" />。风暴发展成热带气旋后产生的影响很小，主要只是停电和道路湿滑，[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]有一人在风暴相关的交通事故中丧生<ref name="Canada" />。
